{"tid":1936864,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(傻撚左) 原來今日元朗班狗手持M16步槍荷槍實彈介備","createTime":"2020-03-21T13:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T09:40:26.000Z","uid":222970,"like":21,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ac763e763b50e1907478c0a7341e09d48cb5efad","tid":1936864,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"仆你個街 如果走火點算<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111587046907016/posts/240910390641347/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111587046907016%2Fposts%2F240910390641347%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=b06b0278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111587046907016/posts/240910390641347/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fYDq4xz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfYDq4xz.jpg&h=b48482b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【3.21 元朗721事件8個月｜防暴手持步槍｜大量警力駐守元朗站】<br />\n<br />\n元朗站即時<br />\n721元朗黑夜事件8個月，港鐵未有封站，只開放部份出入口，元朗站G 出口有大批防暴聽從指揮官簡報，部份疑手持M16-A1單發式步槍戒備，嚴陣以待。<br />\n<br />\n反觀站內只見軍裝警員與港鐵職員，元朗站外亦有多架衝鋒車駐守。<br />\n<br />\n攝：Nepo, Karen<br />\n<br />\n _______________________<br />\n訂閱 Yt 頻道: PSHKmediaofficial<br />\nIG : pshkinc<br />\nTw : OfficalPshk<br />\n<br />\n如果想支持PSHK記者<br />\n歡迎大家以PayPal / 轉數快資助形式捐款畀我哋<br />\nPaypal link : paypal .me/pshk100<br />\n轉數快：9992611"},{"pid":"fd9520a238c984a89fb4b9c52cc6acc19227e18e","tid":1936864,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T13:31:48.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"18582d881781ef0fcc808e30b8155ebd3d297164","tid":1936864,"uid":24331,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T13:32:23.000Z","msg":"同poly 個役一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ddfa1efd52901659fa0403f15f2338f8327952","tid":1936864,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T13:32:35.000Z","